text:
- [Narrator] Amazon QuickSight
Embedded is an intuitive,

fast, and invaluable approach
to adding data-rich visuals

and interactive dashboards
into your applications.
These can empower your end users
to make more informed decisions

by enhancing your
application's user experience,
with insights right where they are needed.

Start delivering advanced
analytics in minutes
with QuickSight's one-click embedding.
You can make sure your embedded content
matches your application's look and feel,

using QuickSight themes
and powerful JavaScript.
The process is simple too,

because there are no
servers to set up or manage.
Then, taking ease a step further,

automatic software updates
ensure there's no ongoing effort
to maintain your applications,

as they seamlessly scale
from tens, to thousands,

to hundreds of thousands of
users without infrastructure.
And, you only pay for what you use.

To get started, all you need
to do is build your dashboards

and use QuickSight's
one-click embedding option

to copy and paste them into
your application or webpage.
It's really that simple.

Put your data to work today
with Amazon QuickSight Embedded.
